==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''macroevolution'''
# large-scale patterns or processes in the history of [[life]], including the [[origin]]s of [[novel]] [[organismal]] [[design]]s, [[evolutionary]] [[trend]]s, [[adaptive]] [[radiation]]s and [[extinction]]s

===Usage note===
The term '''macro'''evolution was introduced to distinguish large-scale patterns of evolution from genetic and small-scale factors, which are termed '''micro'''evolution.

